Bitcoin, the controversial cyber currency catching the eye — for better or worse — of some of the world's most prominent investors, got a boost late last week when the leader of a well known hedge fund expressed his enthusiasm about the currency's future. But Bitcoin still is a long way from mainstream hedge fund adoption.
